{"tid":2155443,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有人問我海外手足除左twitter邊到可以打國際線 我咁樣答佢","createTime":"2020-08-13T19:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T05:51:36.000Z","uid":232848,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"547cabf7ee19a6edaee275e2be90911b9ceb0fa8","tid":2155443,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:35:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/NOW4humanity/status/1293961345256300547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNOW4humanity%2Fstatus%2F1293961345256300547&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=7cfd115f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNOW4humanity%2Fstatus%2F1293961345256300547&h=1c1c1505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/NOW4humanity/status/1293961345256300547</a><br />\n答案就係每個禮拜五去當地既<span class=\"red\"><strong>支那大使館</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由7月到依家一直都有組織搞Fridays for freedom集會,但係都唔算多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要好少亞洲面孔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LhcQZm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LhcQZm.png&h=c58f8cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tygw6xJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftygw6xJ.jpg&h=8604718a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VdYb6xM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdYb6xM.jpg&h=71598fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWsTAsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWsTAsT.jpg&h=910877bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今個禮拜支共又不停加速 拉左肥佬黎同周庭令到日本同國際都有好大迴響<br />\n一定要食住個勢煲返大香港既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">香港本地依家做唔到既野 就由海外既手足接力</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab0d440a666a61075138f1a013ebe8de8cd02be","tid":2155443,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54b4b0aae5f40bf64703c064bd69a5ec92e921c","tid":2155443,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29efb8e14aa2f3e9778b6a7438ad6f65d193a6a8","tid":2155443,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d024aa4169d2e0eee3d3fb2c2355c144fa46869","tid":2155443,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e926e3e5e97e72ba9495b9e9d851ee01eac255a5","tid":2155443,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785a36f5c09c6f8378d922921e71bf3114cbf425","tid":2155443,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:39:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c30a36fdbeac8fdd45918586c1be465edc5c28c9","tid":2155443,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T19:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34b0901b21933053264ccb11012f22b08221858","tid":21